(1. INTRODUCTION) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Rail Vikas Nigam Limited \(RVNL\), Southern Zone, invites online tenders from) Tj T*
(eligible contractors for the following work:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Work Name     : Construction of ROB \(5-span prestressed concrete bridge,) Tj T*
(                total span 120 m\) at Km 134+600, Mysuru Bengaluru Doubling,) Tj T*
(                Mandya District, Karnataka. Includes approach roads \(1.2 km) Tj T*
(                each side\), retaining walls, and railway track protection works.) Tj T*
(Estimated Cost : Rs. 18,50,00,000/- \(Rs. Eighteen Crore Fifty Lakh\)) Tj T*
(EMD            : Rs. 37,00,000/-) Tj T*
(Performance Security : 5% of contract value) Tj T*
(Completion Period : 24 months from date of commencement) Tj T*
(Defect Liability : 36 months) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(NOTE: This NIT includes CORRIGENDUM NO. 1 \(dated 07 June 2026\) and) Tj T*
(CORRIGENDUM NO. 2 \(dated 19 June 2026\). Bidders MUST read all three sections.) Tj T*
(The latest corrigendum supersedes all prior versions on amended items.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
