() Tj T*
(3. SCOPE OF WORK) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.1 Bridge Structure \(Main Span\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  \(a\) 5-span prestressed concrete box girder bridge, total length 120 m) Tj T*
(      \(span arrangement 24+24+24+24+24 m\), 7.5 m carriageway + 2x1.5 m) Tj T*
(      footpaths, designed for 2-lane NH loading.) Tj T*
